The Google search engine has created many problems in my professional   
career due to keeping the above mentioned website in its records.

still keeps it in its memory.

records and since the data is wrong but connected with my name, I believe 

my rights to privacy are being violated by Google.

Please let me know what can be done on Google side in order to finally  
delete the unrequested link.

Kind regards,

Simona Genatova
